Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:07.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是什麽颜色 男孩又是什麽颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:12.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩是红色 男孩是什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:19.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}某种颜色的女孩和某种颜色的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:24.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果邂逅 那在他们之间会产生什麽颜色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定 还是纯白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:30.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如同新展开的画布一般纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在未来才能决定颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:37.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那恋爱的颜色一定是白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:44.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能将两人的颜色染上的透彻的纯粹的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:37.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}纯白色的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:35.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 果然还是迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我又犯老毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:43.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在连自己在什麽地方都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 迷路还是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃那麽漂亮 我一直都很担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用担心的 迷路的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你迷路的话 只要我能找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:01.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 迷路的话只要让哥哥找到就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 能照到那附近的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起来没什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是是旧市街吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非那里有各务卖场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:01.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:32.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 现在在什麽地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:53.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个… 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}离开刚才的地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:05:00.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 被一只奇怪的生物所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:08.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要再到处走了 会让我找不着的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:12.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我知道了 我不再到处乱走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}（请给电池充电）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}电池没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 附近有没有什麽标志物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:26.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:31.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都是围墙 还有就是能看到山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:32.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结女的山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会马上找到你的 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我不会乱走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心 我马上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 没什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前辈 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}欢迎回来 你到底去了什麽地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}金木樨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:47.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我答应哥哥不到处乱走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:53.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:08:00.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您所拨打的电话不在服务区或已关机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 瓜生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 是的 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:39.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}给你 是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:55.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事 爱理和我一起撑着伞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 是谁 刚才的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 爱理的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:01.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:03.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那这个手机是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:04.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 樱乃 那你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}换我接电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我叫濑名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重新正式问候一下 我叫瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真对不起 我妹妹给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实我也迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:34.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}心里也有些不安 反而是樱乃帮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 你要是道谢 我也会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}两个人都还迷着路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:43.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是路痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才的 可不是值得笑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 从那里能看到什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里是上坡的路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}远远可以看到街市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:06.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那条路的相反方向 是朝着山里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}朝着山一直向前走的话 应该可以到公园的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:15.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 哥哥现在在什麽地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也在旧市街
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在公园的西门附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 进公园以後的路 我也清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃怎麽样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:45.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 再过一会就能见到哥哥了 再加油一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麽了 连哥哥也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过说得也是 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}濑名?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是樱乃的哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:19.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:28.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 真的万分的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 反而是我得到了很多帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爱理 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还想再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 因为 我们已经是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 热水马上就要烧好了 先进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:12.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差点就要得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天开始就是十月了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:41.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也来洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我在里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事 我们是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可能没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:52.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被雨淋湿 身体冰凉的兄妹 在一起取暖...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我说不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爸爸和妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已经出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像接下来的一段时间会很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:36.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:41.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各务卖场的鱼店 有打折的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这就是昨天的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真正要买的是这个才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:48.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:54.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天是第一天 不能给哥哥随便的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢你 樱乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:11.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}琳琅满目昂贵商品的各务卖场 和平常的我们完全无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:23.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 路痴的樱乃冒着迷路的危险 到那里去购物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全都是为了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃冬天的校服 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4个月没见了吧 哥哥的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的就没什麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 樱乃穿这衣服很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 准太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 是新吾啊 还有樱乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:03.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就让我们出发去新学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}少女和她的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:14.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下来我们就要踏上的路就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:20.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不错呢 这样可疑的举止 我都燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是被樱乃给丢下了 新吾你要怎麽办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 听说准太有婚约者了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 真尖锐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好的吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和女... 女生们的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}觉得 好像有些要窒息一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那句话 我的立场怎麽办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:17.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我们的母校 在新市街的各务台学园
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为陷入经营困境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在结姬女子学园的提议下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}进行了学校合并
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 说起旧市街的结女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结姬女子学园是历史悠长的大小姐学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:38.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}从十月份开始在那里实验性地 将一年级二年级选拔出来的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作为试验生就读结女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:46.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没错 我和樱乃 还有准人都是其中的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}名门女校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:58.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麽疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个… 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:18.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安洁从初次见面的人 得到我回来了的答覆还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:23.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}您一定很能干吧 安洁莉娜大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:27.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非您是华族或者贵族的後代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没错 您的英姿依稀散发出高贵的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:36.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能让我心这样砰砰直跳的 好久都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是很绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安洁都陶醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}结女的欢迎Neta吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}觉得因太过吃惊而逃跑的人也会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个不用担心 我会带好路的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你是 结女的女仆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是 教工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:06.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 虽然让我来负责带路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我安洁 是野生女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女仆?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}野生女仆?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:21.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字是安洁莉娜·菜夏·史威尔 以後我们就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你们是暂时来上学的试验生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:32.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}现在就带你们去讲堂 请移步这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:43.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过这真的是华丽的校舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:47.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没想到还是野生女仆出没的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过连野生女仆都遇到了 应该不会有更值得惊讶的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:15.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个生物 好像在哪里见过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:17.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 椋梨 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好厉害啊 大小姐学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 这里也像是能举办舞会了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然出现女仆来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:43.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}万智老师 上去说几句话比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}振作一点 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是… 年轻的男性有那麽多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你这麽说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:54.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是结女的老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}集合场所在这里就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:06.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 那个… 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:08.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}万智老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学园长马上就要来了 再稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:20.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛… 很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是一直都这麽强势 会不受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别罗嗦了 这样会让各务台的学生等很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我把学园长带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}濑名 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}八冢老师也振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:47.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 真的是太顽固了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道是生理中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽呀 因为宿醉让他人久等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是母亲提出的建议呢 学园合并
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:21:00.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗 我一直觉得是这样的 你是很欢迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才没有欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:04.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.42,0:21:09.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶 您们曾经谋面过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樱乃 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}濑名 是结女的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爱理 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麽 是爱理认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里是我们的学园
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无论学园长是如何决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:43.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但决不是所有的学生都赞同合并的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少我就 不欢迎你们男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为这个结姬女子学园 是女校!

Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 瓜生 你到底在看什麽地方呢
